<subSubSection pageId="101" pageNumber="380" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="101.[741,1333,1793,2216]" pageId="101" pageNumber="380">
Recent studies identified 
<taxonomicName box="[1120,1293,1911,1940]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Vesperimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fraterculus">P. fraterculus</taxonomicName>
as a species separate from PF. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[1147,1252,1947,1980]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eremicus">eremicus</taxonomicName>
, with 
<taxonomicName box="[742,908,1986,2019]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Vesperimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fraterculus">P. fraterculus</taxonomicName>
distributed on west side of the Colorado River and 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[1027,1164,2025,2058]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eremicus">P. eremicus</taxonomicName>
on east side of the river. 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Miller" baseAuthorityYear="1892" box="[920,1206,2069,2098]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fraterculus">Peromyscus fraterculus</taxonomicName>
is in the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Baird" baseAuthorityYear="1857" box="[744,848,2108,2137]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="eremicus">eremicus</taxonomicName>
species group. Allocation of subspecies is somewhat unclear. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="101" pageNumber="380" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6760936" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6760936" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6760936/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="101" pageNumber="380" startId="101.[742,914,2187,2216]" targetBox="[127,718,1798,2214]" targetPageId="101">
